{"tid":11923,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"人大左，愈來愈享受自己孤獨一個","createTime":"2016-11-29T12:43:49.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-24T05:03:28.000Z","uid":39109,"like":50,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9dba9f957a0f84baf8e715f2da9d9195d8511d06","tid":11923,"uid":39109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T12:43:49.000Z","msg":"以前細個中學成日都要同班frd一齊，放學唔肯返屋企要周圍行，大時大節就一定要出街，生日一定要約好多朋友食飯慶祝。<br />\n<br />\n到之後拍拖，成個世界就得男/女朋友一個，日日都要見，食飯睇戲、去邊都要一齊，見少一陣好似會死咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到而家廿幾歲人，無再拍拖無再返學，日日返工放工，全日野都唔講多幾句，除左食就係訓，放假唔想出街，覺得出面好多人好逼。連朋友約都唔想出去，收工/放假寧願自己一個行下食下野，搭下車上下網咁就一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n生日愈來愈少人記得，愈來愈唔想過生日，覺得自己好老咁。節日永遠都收埋自己係屋企對住四幅牆，但都無乜感覺，反而覺得好平靜好享受自己一個既時間。<br />\n<br />\n究竟係我享受自己一個定係生活逼使我要去享受呢？無所謂。因為我早已經習慣了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcfc242bde39754d9b6f7945d9765846fd741ef9","tid":11923,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T12:45:16.000Z","msg":"pmed"},{"pid":"c6f0f1070e4d391961e25d9013b26e735ab981da","tid":11923,"uid":21355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T12:46:29.000Z","msg":"yes<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2f264a6b767a9eb8c085d1abb84cdae4216cde2","tid":11923,"uid":39109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T12:49:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>pmed</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nLihkg無pm 架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8f07778d500f8f0a016b8cfc7c9f3be3c65c592","tid":11923,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T12:50:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>pmed</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nLihkg無pm 架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n幫你推咋ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58e3fad63cb040c25e1643934495365e8f9ff031","tid":11923,"uid":39109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T12:50:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>yes<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打還好嗎"},{"pid":"2fedb587c3e2d19ba9948d065b903e9455179965","tid":11923,"uid":12755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T12:50:58.000Z","msg":"篇野咁熟口面嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43ac1e086b705993b41fb92708c4f136456e3824","tid":11923,"uid":39109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T12:51:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>pmed</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nLihkg無pm 架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n幫你推咋ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f31ac2a724a47816481900374e58c24866444387","tid":11923,"uid":39109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T12:51:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>篇野咁熟口面嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我岩岩打架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1336909c2cd40fc169097dedfbaa92e262684cc1","tid":11923,"uid":21355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T12:52:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>yes<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打還好嗎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以前好鍾意同frd出街 依家就淨係搵籍口唔想出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3399036c6c06043a1ac73805750777c616be601b","tid":11923,"uid":39109,"like":0,"dislike":0,