 有時仲要講大話呃朋友話唔舒服<br />\n完全唔想出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己一個仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n淨係想做廢青咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係。再係咁會無哂朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇晒就算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申1年前開始已經冇同以前既朋友聯絡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a10b3667ff9f7ad46369ed99023bbdd64a9a5a3","tid":11923,"uid":2792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T13:09:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eb2eaa2d6c54dd07cd1d1f9ae91d03126b52969","tid":11923,"uid":41859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T13:09:27.000Z","msg":"享受就唔sad face 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1134626ab77be219f8a9bc39928765375592037","tid":11923,"uid":39109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T13:09:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係 覺得既然自得其樂 點解又要自尋煩惱</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當然有時都會好懷愐以前既生活，覺得有朋友有拍拖好似好充實咁 但係關係既野始終會變 <br />\n唔只愛情係咁 連朋友都係咁<br />\n好多年朋友都可以話斷聯絡就斷聯絡<br />\n既然係咁點解仲要付出咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d511c5a8c9299f97c4ae299e6a81c8914c29f625","tid":11923,"uid":16528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T13:10:16.000Z","msg":"都市人既寂寞"},{"pid":"ea016b51db907929e8683e4369d1b71add26cb74","tid":11923,"uid":29371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T13:13:24.000Z","msg":"寧願自己一個都唔想勉強自己去迎合一啲所謂既朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1476d7d78e7f1b4ef0fdda8049526b0e44e3749d","tid":11923,"uid":39315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T13:14:09.000Z","msg":"唔知點解人愈大愈鐘意同人相處有個距離，唔鐘意同人太熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"086f4b1f8683e7b4abc6e7dfcf80f33e1eb41501","tid":11923,"uid":39109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T13:15:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>非常認同<br />\n又唔好話孤獨既<br />\n鐘意自己享受姐<br />\n<br />\n我自從番左工之後呢種感覺強烈左好多<br />\n特別有時同仲係大學生既人講野真係好睇得到個分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n絲打我認得你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我以前係高登係cd-rom黎，不過都上左好多年<br />\n<br />\n我都覺，可能真係因為返左工 同班同事會傾下計但點都唔會好似以前同d同學咁熟成日一齊玩<br />\n以前返學好多野講 而家變左全日都好少講野咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每日最享受就係搭巴士返工放工既時間，可以一個人諗下野<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9571e0f5692321448a3157031980d98da5743798","tid":11923,"uid":28769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T13:17:01.000Z","msg":"做乜都係一個人，但想有個時刻都陪係身邊既女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f62bb1c0ad48127da33d732822dcac20e50763a0","tid":11923,"uid":39109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T13:17:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Same here<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> welcome"},{"pid":"7080c149750665d74ce11485dd1528f721ab89d0","tid":11923,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T13:17:22.000Z","msg":"由細到大都孤獨一個，無得比較，sor :-)"},{"pid":"0c562a6ad1ec02ef705549ed79e83fe8b5dec7a9","tid":11923,"uid":35888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T13:18:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>由細到大都孤獨一個，無得比較，sor :-)</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSame here"},{"pid":"346fc68246b20