ss=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申1年前開始已經冇同以前既朋友聯絡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一個朋友都無聯絡？？"},{"pid":"a7f68aeb7189362267ecbe2223ec88f077173c49","tid":11923,"uid":39109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T13:48:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>享受就唔sad face 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自欺欺人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d1d375d60d698939658c8a916812ff54b1e1602","tid":11923,"uid":7764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T13:50:50.000Z","msg":"不要再說了.jpg<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f8e79ff17b004f95eab02a4dc368bea02b56507","tid":11923,"uid":39109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T13:51:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>寧願自己一個都唔想勉強自己去迎合一啲所謂既朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都覺，有時同以前d同學明明好耐無見出黎食飯<br />\n明明無乜野講唔再好似以前咁 都要夾硬出黎「聚舊」<br />\n成餐飯食完好似無食過咁<br />\n會心諗究竟出黎做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f11608ad6af6a3a143cbc9587ef06c4bccf59197","tid":11923,"uid":22374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T13:52:08.000Z","msg":"生活迫人呀巴打，大家一起加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daa9db043ad7fcb236f554f9b1426dfd5e04d228","tid":11923,"uid":2154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T13:52:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都係 覺得既然自得其樂 點解又要自尋煩惱</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當然有時都會好懷愐以前既生活，覺得有朋友有拍拖好似好充實咁 但係關係既野始終會變 <br />\n唔只愛情係咁 連朋友都係咁<br />\n好多年朋友都可以話斷聯絡就斷聯絡<br />\n既然係咁點解仲要付出咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有時覺得人與人之間既關係真係得表面 除左佢之外"},{"pid":"3bc879ecf7a4dc25a1ec4b6e04d5cdde280e680c","tid":11923,"uid":6382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T13:52:54.000Z","msg":"I know that feel bro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ad4ea1c46d547a379575912666988740a858e97","tid":11923,"uid":39109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T13:53:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔知點解人愈大愈鐘意同人相處有個距離，唔鐘意同人太熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係咁 返工果陣好唔想同同事講咁多自己既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3d1f7b5f6e97c292a2b957eb9c95801ed361c0e","tid":11923,"uid":22739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T13:54:44.000Z","msg":"Same feeling bro <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31a7acf5ed7108b728e75a743ccd086762a2b081","tid":11923,"uid":39109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T13:56:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做乜都係一個人，但想有個時刻都陪係身邊既女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我有時都會咁諗<br />\n但一諗到以前自己毫無保留咁付出一切去愛一個人<br />\n到頭來俾人當垃圾咁嫌棄扔走既時候 就寧願繼續自己孤獨一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e12d823613a6f372eae6b86068d7fd8e0f0631d","tid":11923,"uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T13:56:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n絲打我認得你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我以前係高登係cd-rom黎，不過都上左好多年<br />\n<br />\n我都覺，可能真係因為返左工 同班同事會傾下計但點都唔會好似以前同d同學咁熟成日一齊玩<br />\n以前返學好多野講 而家變左全日都好少講野咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每日最享受就係搭巴士返工放工既時間，可以一個人諗下野<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我係巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nAnyway好彩番工唔叫辛苦同同事都有講有笑叫做冇壓力啦<br />\n真心搭車同臨訓前果陣真係最舒服<br />\n放假搵下野食睇下劇不知幾舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n重點係我都幾鐘意咁既生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過唔知會唔會搵到個都係咁諗既女朋友姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb023cf334e67684700e0284a8e119bb9a3dd1fe","tid":11923,"uid":37005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T13:56:58.000Z","msg":"agger<br />\n我都係咁 愈黎愈唔鍾意熱鬧嘈嘈閉咁<br />\n好鍾意獨處 連生日都想靜靜咁過"},{"pid":"0152b5df04d247a2f8bff54141bd10394e706d26","tid":11923,"uid":39109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T13:58:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>由細到大都孤獨一個，無得比較，sor :-)</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSame here</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無兄弟姊妹無朋友？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n灰處未算灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/south_bear.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bb1a3318321b66aa39d287d1bf95f090182f2c9","tid":11923,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T13:58:40.000Z","msg":"搵d興趣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4c1b861bd2a6657bca9db0eb87ccdeafe379f43","tid":11923,"uid":28769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T14:00:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>做乜都係一個人，但想有個時刻都陪係身邊既女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我有時都會咁諗<br />\n但一諗到以前自己毫無保留咁付出一切去愛一個人<br />\n到頭來俾人當垃圾咁嫌棄扔走既時候 就寧願繼續自己孤獨一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好多時有感覺完係埋一齊又係另一件事，我會主張有感覺就試左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54437d5efab6fc4e1609d965cd4d3a8a893d8ac4","tid":11923,"uid":39109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T14:00:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你過左30歲就唔會再有人搵你，結婚既結婚，生仔既生仔，一出黎只會傾湊仔經悶撚死你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲有幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n身邊已經有朋友生左<br />\n可能到佢個仔幾歲既時候 我仲係自己一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f78ff57527bbc9ff47160867e2f0a531b4a14925","tid":11923,"uid":9153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T14:01:49.000Z","msg":"愈來愈鐘意收埋自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"084165e5b65a1692579d5dec0fbbdcc495a91ab3","tid":11923,"uid":6382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T14:02:31.000Z","msg":"我都係想搵個女朋友仔陪我啫"},{"pid":"b8cf8b65bbffdaf041fa8a11d4f7fb59303eb17d","tid":11923,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T14:07:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>yes<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打還好嗎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以前好鍾意同frd出街 依家就淨係搵籍口唔想出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係咁 有時仲要講大話呃朋友話唔舒服<br />\n完全唔想出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己一個仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n淨係想做廢青咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係。再係咁會無哂朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇晒就算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申1年前開始已經冇同以前既朋友聯絡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一個朋友都無聯絡？？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4217988779cbb4960fb492fec8dfd1d637d0840c","tid":11923,"uid":16239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T14:08:13.000Z","msg":"Agger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eeae009a2580cf85323945a4f2156a0ee5a8de6","tid":11923,"uid":26082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T14:09:42.000Z","msg":"我都係咁 但總有一些朋友想搵我....我又唔好意思拒絕，其實我只想一個人做尖休息食野...."},{"pid":"20aa8f27f4271d42bb0ecb1dfa612ef6b0355f21","tid":11923,"uid":9619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T14:12:31.000Z","msg":"又未算享受 但完全唔介意自己一個"},{"pid":"2fba2b52a7335333e0149b6874783234972e1b3a","tid":11923,"uid":29281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T14:14:51.000Z","msg":"其實自己一個更開心"},{"pid":"5b294f74ee7730d29578c6c6cef018264d7913fe","tid":11923,"uid":38371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T14:38:18.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"de4cad33a6cf0e06cec37bb4cd496fea962c1f78","tid":11923,"uid":39109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T14:39:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>生活迫人呀巴打，大家一起加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大家咁話<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e3cd2af92ff3a008108e8df0675fef3936cc9cd","tid":11923,"uid":39109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T14:40:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我都係 覺得既然自得其樂 點解又要自尋煩惱</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當然有時都會好懷愐以前既生活，覺得有朋友有拍拖好似好充實咁 但係關係既野始終會變 <br />\n唔只愛情係咁 連朋友都係咁<br />\n好多年朋友都可以話斷聯絡就斷聯絡<br />\n既然係咁點解仲要付出咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有時覺得人與人之間既關係真係得表面 除左佢之外</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係呀 曾經幾好朋友最尾都斷絕來往<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除左佢係指邊個？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a2eb9f104b1db585f0b0924a571ca53cf491361","tid":11923,"uid":39109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T14:44:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n絲打我認得你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我以前係高登係cd-rom黎，不過都上左好多年<br />\n<br />\n我都覺，可能真係因為返左工 同班同事會傾下計但點都唔會好似以前同d同學咁熟成日一齊玩<br />\n以前返學好多野講 而家變左全日都好少講野咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每日最享受就係搭巴士返工放工既時間，可以一個人諗下野<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我係巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nAnyway好彩番工唔叫辛苦同同事都有講有笑叫做冇壓力啦<br />\n真心搭車同臨訓前果陣真係最舒服<br />\n放假搵下野食睇下劇不知幾舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n重點係我都幾鐘意咁既生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過唔知會唔會搵到個都係咁諗既女朋友姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我見你紅字<br />\n其實都係 靜靜地仲好<br />\n好怕搭車果陣遇到d人大大聲講野 會覺得好唔耐煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一定會有既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 時候未到姐！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bdac2cc276b9e239c7f791aa2077c36b1a2ea7f","tid":11923,"uid":39109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T14:48:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>agger<br />\n我都係咁 愈黎愈唔鍾意熱鬧嘈嘈閉咁<br />\n好鍾意獨處 連生日都想靜靜咁過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係，完全唔想慶祝<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食餐飯就算<br />\n我d frd仲話要收生日禮物 我覺得好煩<br />\n咁大個人仲要咩禮物姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90fcfbbaa7ecc2dc866d35621ec2fa79ad6fb853","tid":11923,"uid":15342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T14:49:38.000Z","msg":"自己一個唔洗帶住面具做人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"506060c6cb2f0ab8981c89ad760908fc7af428b6","tid":11923,"uid":39109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T14:50:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搵d興趣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前想學畫畫學學器<br />\n但又覺得自己年紀大 呢d野應該細細個學<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又唔想付出金錢去學 唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4805094c08a80ad5300628c9a358091f111d177f","tid":11923,"uid":39109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T14:52:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>愈來愈鐘意收埋自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一樣，wtsapp可以全日都無人搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3833c6655a65365a379d5047a24f5ec8247340aa","tid":11923,"uid":4422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T14:52:38.000Z","msg":"由一出世就過住咁既生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a57e4c96e85dfc6c24dc893adf1f3f37ca2ba4e","tid":11923,"uid":39395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T14:54:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"350fa74242552d1e4af546f465a7f3f102400aed","tid":11923,"uid":34415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T14:59:04.000Z","msg":"