img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到依家yr3 又唔係乜都唔玩 <br />\n但真係無哂主動想識人/去玩既心<br />\n因為自己一個實在太舒服"},{"pid":"960960c8d9c90823205f552893ea2e7a0da140b7","tid":11923,"uid":29645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T07:20:38.000Z","msg":"我享受唔到<br />\n去到大學最後一年先黎後悔自己乜野都冇參加冇玩過<br />\n剩係番學放學<br />\n識既人冇幾個<br />\n拖冇拍過<br />\n望住個whatsapp冇人搵<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好撚後悔呀吊"},{"pid":"3fe563fb03a0cf25e3ad0b91567c05e321f30a51","tid":11923,"uid":29645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T07:24:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點睇由大學yr1就已經開始係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到依家yr3 又唔係乜都唔玩 <br />\n但真係無哂主動想識人/去玩既心<br />\n因為自己一個實在太舒服</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我當時係諗住果種友誼好似好假咁<br />\n所以咩都唔玩<br />\n諗住有個我認為係知己既朋友就夠<br />\n點知係我一廂情願<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}